    <div id="FAQ">
      <h2> FAQ! </h2>
      <h3> Q: What is OpenInvite?</h3>
      <h3> A: This app is designed to help you connect with friends in your area! </h3><br>
	  <h3> Q: Is OpenInvite free? </h3>
	  <h3> A: OpenInvite and all its services are completely free of charge to you. </h3><br>
      <h3> Q: How do I Create an event? </h3>
      <h3> A: There are two places from which you can create an event. On the sidebar, navigate to either Home or My Events,
              then press the Create Event button. This will bring up a form that you can use to share your event. </h3><br>
      <h3> Q: Help! I accidentally joined the wrong event! How do I unjoin? </h3>
      <h3> A: Simply click the Cancel button that appears to the left of your friend's event. </h3><br>
	  <h3> Q: How do I change my email address?. </h3>
	  <h3> A: You can change your email address anytime by clicking on 'Edit' button located in your profile Page.
			  You can access your profile page by clicking on your picture on top of navigation bar. </h3><br>
	  <h3> Q: What do we do to keep your information secure?  </h3>
	  <h3> A: We do our best to keep your personal data secure. We have put in place reasonable physical and technical
			  measures to safeguard the information we collect in connection with all our users.</h3><br>
    </div>

